About us
ESTABLISHED IN 2005
Located in the heart of Coconut Grove, Oasis was one of the first hookah lounges in Miami, established in 2005. With over 50 selections of hookah flavors, food, beers, and other drinks, Oasis is the ideal spot for a relaxed weeknight hangout or a great party on the weekends. In addition to our selection at the bar, Oasis features pool tables and indoor and outdoor seating.
We are a 21+ establishment and request ID for all services.
Our Services is available for private parties. Please
contact us
for more information.
